    "course_title": "THEORY OF ELASTICITY",
    "description": "Equations of elasticity in curvilinear and rectangular coordinates; two dimensional problems; problems of prismatic bars; variational methods and energy principles; complex variable and numerical methods; thermal stress problems. Knowledge of advanced mechanics of materials [such asE\u00a0M\u00a0A\u00a0506] and vector calculus [such asMATH\u00a0321] strongly encouraged.",
